column3:
Whew, an excellent, merciless breakdown...
A bit too cosmetic, beautifying on a cellular level, but...
Even I need time to recover from all this...

This is about my time limit per title... Huh?
Oh, you're... No way?!

Ahh, such a cool beauty.
It just screams "you worthless cat".

But just you wait. I'll do my best.
I have lots of other invasion plans.

Will you stop supervising your useless subordinates?
No? Okay, I get that.

Well, goodbye everyone!
Next time, I'll really go all out!
